abstract: >-
  A vendor-neutral vault of agent skills. Each skill is a local
  SKILL.md file under skills/ — frontmatter, prompt, example, and a
  "When NOT to use" section. Drop into Claude, Codex, Cursor, Continue,
  or any Markdown-reading agent. The external-index/ directory keeps a
  discovery list of upstream repos for skills we have not yet mirrored.
